snippet.title: 4 Luxury Roja’s | Amber Aoud, Danger, Fruity Aoud & Chypré Extraordinaire | Fragrance Reflection
snippet.description:
NEW Series 'Fragrance Reflection'

Similar to the 'Sampling Madness series' but more of an overview and small discussion of what I sampled in the last few days or weeks. In these type of video’s I will report on latest discoveries in fragance land of which I wasn't able to record a first impressions video. Occasionally I might throw in some chit chat.


Fragrances mentioned / timeline:

3:34 Roja Dove Amber Aoud
7:58 Roja Dove Danger pour homme 
10:27 Roja Dove Fruity Aoud
13:06 Roja Dove Chypré Extraordinaire

Perfume store mentioned:
https://www.lamaisonduparfum.be/

Find me on Instagram: @fragrancewithsteve

Fanmail and business inquires: fragranceswithsteve@gmail.com

Thanks for watching!
